How Did We Get Here?

Just like almost every other profession -- medicine,
law, and politics included -- affiliate marketing has a
checkered past. Worse, affiliate marketing seems to have a
checkered present. Where's the problem -- and the solution?
In corporate organizational structures.

http://clickz.com/article/cz.4003.html




