An Affiliate Marketing Primer: Chapter III

You've set the affiliate program's objective and figured
out the offer. You've found the right outsourcing partner,
measured the results, and marketed the program. What's
next? Care for and feed affiliates -- or if they're
fraudsters, weed them out.

http://clickz.com/article/cz.4005.html





