The Proof's in the Presentation

A presentation to an investor can border on pleading -- or
worse, it can become an inquisition. Greg and Emily offer
some basic tips that every entrepreneur should know to make
a solid presentation -- whether to investors, a board, or
the staff.


http://clickz.com/article/cz.4002.html




